graph TB
    subgraph "Feast Feature Store"
        Operator[Feast Operator<br/>Kubernetes Operator]

        subgraph "Services"
            OnlineServer[Feature Server Online<br/>HTTP/gRPC 80:6566]
            OfflineServer[Feature Server Offline<br/>HTTP 80:8815]
            Registry[Registry Service<br/>gRPC 80:6570]
            RegistryREST[Registry REST<br/>HTTP 80:6572]
            Transform[Transformation Service<br/>gRPC 80:6569]
            UI[UI Service<br/>HTTP 80:8888]
        end

        Operator -->|manages| OnlineServer
        Operator -->|manages| OfflineServer
        Operator -->|manages| Registry
        Operator -->|manages| RegistryREST
        Operator -->|manages| Transform
        Operator -->|manages| UI

        OnlineServer -->|queries metadata| Registry
        OfflineServer -->|queries metadata| Registry
        OnlineServer -->|transforms features| Transform
        UI -->|queries metadata| RegistryREST
    end

    subgraph "CRDs"
        FeatureStoreCR[FeatureStore CR<br/>feast.dev/v1]
    end

    subgraph "Storage Backends"
        OnlineDB[Online Store<br/>Redis/PostgreSQL/DynamoDB<br/>6379/5432 TCP]
        OfflineDB[Offline Store<br/>BigQuery/Snowflake/S3<br/>443 HTTPS TLS 1.2+]
        RegistryDB[Registry Backend<br/>PostgreSQL/S3/GCS<br/>5432/443 TCP]
    end

    subgraph "Clients"
        MLApp[ML Application<br/>Real-time Inference]
        TrainingJob[ML Training Job<br/>Historical Features]
        StreamApp[Stream Processing<br/>Feature Push]
    end

    User[User] -->|creates| FeatureStoreCR
    FeatureStoreCR -->|watched by| Operator
    Operator -->|creates| OnlineServer
    Operator -->|creates| OfflineServer

    MLApp -->|/get-online-features| OnlineServer
    TrainingJob -->|HTTP request| OfflineServer
    StreamApp -->|/push| OnlineServer

    OnlineServer -->|read/write| OnlineDB
    OfflineServer -->|query| OfflineDB
    Registry -->|read/write| RegistryDB
    OnlineServer -->|materialize| OfflineDB

    subgraph "External Services"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443 HTTPS TLS 1.2+]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraping]
        Istio[Service Mesh Istio<br/>Optional mTLS]
    end

    Operator -->|reconcile| K8sAPI
    OnlineServer -->|metrics 8000/TCP| Prometheus
    Operator -->|metrics 8443/TCP| Prometheus
    OnlineServer -.->|optional| Istio
    OfflineServer -.->|optional| Istio

    style Operator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OnlineServer fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style OfflineServer fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style Registry fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style RegistryREST fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style Transform fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style UI fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style FeatureStoreCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OnlineDB fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style OfflineDB fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style RegistryDB fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Istio fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
